underlying_goal: To design a new feature for showing live progress and errors for individual models in a multi-model application UI.
primary_success: Effectively used a structured brainstorming process to guide the user from a vague idea ('Show live status') to a concrete, well-defined implementation plan with architectural details and a UI concept.
brief_summary: The user wanted to add live status tracking for models in the UI. Claude initiated a brainstorming session, proposing a UI concept and an architectural approach using streaming SSE events, resulting in a detailed implementation plan.
